<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Karrigan Gangwish</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --cream: #f5f0e8;
      --sand: #e8dfc8;
      --terracotta: #c4735a;
      --terracotta-dark: #a05a44;
      --charcoal: #2a2520;
      --warm-gray: #7a7168;
      --light-warm: #f9f5ef;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      background: var(--cream);
      color: var(--charcoal);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ---- NAV ---- */
    nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.2rem 4rem;
      background: rgba(245,240,232,0.92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sand);
    }

    .nav-logo {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      list-style: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.25s;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--terracotta); }

    /* ---- HERO ---- */
    #hero {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 8rem 4rem 4rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-bg-shape {
      position: absolute;
      top: -10%;
      right: -5%;
      width: 55%;
      height: 110%;
      background: var(--sand);
      border-radius: 40% 0 0 50%;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .hero-text {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s ease both;
    }

    .hero-eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--terracotta);
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    .hero-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 7vw, 6rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      line-height: 1.05;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-name em {
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--terracotta);
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 420px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-contact {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .contact-chip {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--sand);
      border-radius: 50px;
      transition: all 0.25s;
      background: white;
    }

    .contact-chip:hover {
      border-color: var(--terracotta);
      color: var(--terracotta);
      background: var(--light-warm);
    }

    .hero-strengths {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.2s ease both;
      padding-left: 4rem;
    }

    .strengths-label {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .strength-item {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      padding: 0.7rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sand);
      opacity: 0.6;
      transition: opacity 0.3s, color 0.3s;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .strength-item:hover {
      opacity: 1;
      color: var(--terracotta);
    }

    /* ---- SECTIONS ---- */
    section {
      padding: 6rem 4rem;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .section-num {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      color: var(--terracotta);
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--charcoal);
    }

    .section-line {
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--sand);
      margin-left: auto;
    }

    /* ---- EXPERIENCE ---- */
    #experience { background: var(--light-warm); }

    .exp-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .exp-card {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 220px 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 3rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--sand);
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s, transform 0.6s;
    }

    .exp-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .exp-card:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }

    .exp-meta { padding-top: 0.25rem; }

    .exp-period {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--terracotta);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .exp-location {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
    }

    .exp-role {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .exp-company {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--terracotta-dark);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .exp-bullets {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .exp-bullets li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      line-height: 1.65;
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
      position: relative;
    }

    .exp-bullets li::before {
      content: '—';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--terracotta);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }

    /* ---- SKILLS ---- */
    #skills { background: var(--charcoal); }

    #skills .section-title { color: var(--cream); }
    #skills .section-num { color: var(--terracotta); }
    #skills .section-line { background: #3a3530; }

    .skills-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .skill-card {
      padding: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid #3a3530;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s, transform 0.6s, border-color 0.3s;
    }

    .skill-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .skill-card:hover { border-color: var(--terracotta); background: rgba(196,115,90,0.06); }

    .skill-card-icon {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .skill-card-title {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: var(--cream);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .skill-tag {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      background: #3a3530;
      border-radius: 3px;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.6rem;
      margin: 0.2rem 0.2rem 0 0;
    }

    /* ---- EDUCATION ---- */
    #education { background: var(--cream); }

    .edu-block {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .edu-main {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s, transform 0.6s;
    }

    .edu-main.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    .edu-school {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .edu-degree {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--terracotta);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .edu-detail {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .gpa-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem;
      background: var(--terracotta);
      color: white;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .edu-side {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s 0.15s, transform 0.6s 0.15s;
    }

    .edu-side.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    .activity-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.2rem; }

    .activity-item {
      padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--sand);
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    .activity-item:hover { border-color: var(--terracotta); }

    .activity-name {
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .activity-role {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--terracotta);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .activity-desc {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ---- VOLUNTEER ---- */
    #volunteer { background: var(--sand); }

    .volunteer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .vol-card {
      background: var(--cream);
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 2rem;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s, transform 0.6s;
    }

    .vol-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    .vol-tag {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--terracotta);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .vol-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: var(--charcoal);
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    }

    .vol-role {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .vol-desc {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    /* ---- FOOTER ---- */
    footer {
      background: var(--charcoal);
      color: var(--warm-gray);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 4rem;
    }

    footer .footer-name {
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: var(--cream);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    footer p { font-size: 0.8rem; margin-top: 0.4rem; }

    footer a {
      color: var(--terracotta);
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* ---- ANIMATIONS ---- */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* ---- RESPONSIVE ---- */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      nav { padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem; }
      .nav-links { gap: 1.5rem; }

      #hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: 7rem 1.5rem 4rem;
        gap: 3rem;
      }

      .hero-bg-shape { display: none; }
      .hero-strengths { padding-left: 0; }

      section { padding: 4rem 1.5rem; }

      .exp-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 0.5rem; }
      .edu-block { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#hero" class="nav-logo">Karrigan Gangwish</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#experience">Experience</a></li>
    <li><a href="#skills">Skills</a></li>
    <li><a href="#education">Education</a></li>
    <li><a href="#volunteer">Service</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg-shape"></div>

  <div class="hero-text">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">International Business · Accounting · Hospitality</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Karrigan<br /><em>Gangwish</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">
      UNL student passionate about people, leadership, and building meaningful experiences—whether in the classroom, on the volleyball court, or in the community.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-contact">
      <a class="contact-chip" href="mailto:kegangwish@gmail.com">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m2 7 10 7 10-7"/></svg>
        kegangwish@gmail.com
      </a>
      <span class="contact-chip">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 1 7 7c0 5-7 13-7 13S5 14 5 9a7 7 0 0 1 7-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="9" r="2.5"/></svg>
        Omaha, NE
      </span>
      <span class="contact-chip">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg>
        (402) 369-9352
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-strengths">
    <p class="strengths-label">CliftonStrengths</p>
    <div class="strength-item">Restorative</div>
    <div class="strength-item">Adaptability</div>
    <div class="strength-item">Includer</div>
    <div class="strength-item">Competition</div>
    <div class="strength-item">Futuristic</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EXPERIENCE -->
<section id="experience">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">01</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Experience</h2>
    <div class="section-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="exp-grid">

    <div class="exp-card">
      <div class="exp-meta">
        <p class="exp-period">Aug 2025 – Present</p>
        <p class="exp-location">Lincoln, NE</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="exp-role">Assistant Teacher</h3>
        <p class="exp-company">Cooper YMCA</p>
        <ul class="exp-bullets">
          <li>Supervised and engaged groups of children using strong communication and classroom management skills to create a safe, structured, and positive environment</li>
          <li>Planned and led creative activities such as arts & crafts, games, and learning exercises to support child development</li>
          <li>Collaborated with staff and communicated with parents in regular meetings to ensure each child's needs were met</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="exp-card">
      <div class="exp-meta">
        <p class="exp-period">Dec 2022 – Jan 2026</p>
        <p class="exp-location">Gretna, NE</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="exp-role">Shift Lead / Server / Busser</h3>
        <p class="exp-company">Tropical Smoothie</p>
        <ul class="exp-bullets">
          <li>Led daily operations in a fast-paced environment by coordinating staff, managing orders, and maintaining efficiency during high-volume shifts</li>
          <li>Delivered high-quality customer service through clear communication and problem-solving, improving customer satisfaction and repeat business</li>
          <li>Trained and supported new employees on daily tasks, cleanliness, food safety standards, and inventory organization</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="exp-card">
      <div class="exp-meta">
        <p class="exp-period">Oct 2024 – Apr 2025</p>
        <p class="exp-location">Gretna, NE</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="exp-role">Volleyball Coach</h3>
        <p class="exp-company">G1 Volleyball</p>
        <ul class="exp-bullets">
          <li>Coached and mentored athletes using leadership and teamwork skills to improve performance, confidence, and game understanding</li>
          <li>Organized and led structured practices focused on skill development, discipline, and team cohesion</li>
          <li>Communicated effectively with players and parents to build a positive, supportive team environment</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- SKILLS -->
<section id="skills">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">02</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
    <div class="section-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="skills-grid">
    <div class="skill-card">
      <div class="skill-card-icon">🗣️</div>
      <h3 class="skill-card-title">Leadership & Communication</h3>
      <span class="skill-tag">Team Coordination</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Parent Communication</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Mentoring</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Classroom Management</span>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-card">
      <div class="skill-card-icon">🌐</div>
      <h3 class="skill-card-title">International Business</h3>
      <span class="skill-tag">Global Mindset</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Cross-Cultural Awareness</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Accounting Minor</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Hospitality Minor</span>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-card">
      <div class="skill-card-icon">💻</div>
      <h3 class="skill-card-title">Technical</h3>
      <span class="skill-tag">Microsoft Excel</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Microsoft PowerPoint</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Microsoft Word</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">CPR Certified</span>
    </div>
    <div class="skill-card">
      <div class="skill-card-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3 class="skill-card-title">Operational</h3>
      <span class="skill-tag">Staff Training</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Inventory Management</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Food Safety</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">High-Volume Operations</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- EDUCATION -->
<section id="education">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">03</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
    <div class="section-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="edu-block">
    <div class="edu-main">
      <h3 class="edu-school">University of Nebraska-Lincoln</h3>
      <p class="edu-degree">Bachelor of Science in Business Administration</p>
      <p class="edu-detail">Major: International Business</p>
      <p class="edu-detail">Minors: Accounting &amp; Hospitality</p>
      <p class="edu-detail">Expected Graduation: May 2029 · Lincoln, NE</p>
      <div class="gpa-badge">
        <svg width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"/></svg>
        GPA: 3.33 / 4.00
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="edu-side">
      <p class="section-num" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">Activities &amp; Involvement</p>
      <ul class="activity-list">
        <li class="activity-item">
          <p class="activity-name">Alpha Chi Omega</p>
          <p class="activity-role">Member · Aug 2025 – Present</p>
          <p class="activity-desc">Participates in philanthropy events, community service, and chapter planning, strengthening teamwork, organization, and leadership.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="activity-item">
          <p class="activity-name">Special Olympics Volleyball</p>
          <p class="activity-role">Volunteer · Nov 2023 – Present</p>
          <p class="activity-desc">Assists athletes with skill development and gameplay through encouragement, patience, and hands-on support.</p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VOLUNTEER -->
<section id="volunteer">
  <div class="section-header">
    <span class="section-num">04</span>
    <h2 class="section-title">Community Service</h2>
    <div class="section-line"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="volunteer-grid">
    <div class="vol-card">
      <p class="vol-tag">Volunteer · Apr 2024 &amp; Apr 2025</p>
      <h3 class="vol-name">Night to Shine</h3>
      <p class="vol-role">Crew Member · Omaha, NE</p>
      <p class="vol-desc">Supported kids with special needs by creating a welcoming and memorable experience—an unforgettable prom night where every guest felt celebrated.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="vol-card">
      <p class="vol-tag">Volunteer · Nov 2023 – Present</p>
      <h3 class="vol-name">Special Olympics Volleyball</h3>
      <p class="vol-role">Athlete Support Volunteer · Gretna, NE</p>
      <p class="vol-desc">Provides ongoing hands-on support to athletes, helping them grow their skills, confidence, and love of the game through patient and encouraging coaching.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="footer-name">Karrigan Gangwish</div>
  <p>International Business · University of Nebraska-Lincoln · Class of 2029</p>
  <p style="margin-top:0.8rem;"><a href="mailto:kegangwish@gmail.com">kegangwish@gmail.com</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp; (402) 369-9352</p>
</footer>

<script>
  // Scroll-reveal for cards
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
    entries.forEach((entry, i) => {
      if (entry.isIntersecting) {
        setTimeout(() => entry.target.classList.add('visible'), i * 100);
        observer.unobserve(entry.target);
      }
    });
  }, { threshold: 0.1 });

  document.querySelectorAll('.exp-card, .skill-card, .edu-main, .edu-side, .vol-card').forEach(el => {
    observer.observe(el);
  });
</script>
</body>
</html>
